```py
my_dict = {
    'Apple': 3,
    'Banana': 1,
    'Orange': 2,
    'Pineapple': 5
    }

for i, key  in enumerate(my_dict.keys()):
    print(i, key)
```

```py
my_dict = {
    'Apple': 3,
    'Banana': 1,
    'Orange': 2,
    'Pineapple': 5
    }

for i, value  in enumerate(my_dict.values()):
